org.sakaiproject.db.cover

Class SqlService

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.sakaiproject.db.cover.SqlService
  • Deprecated. 
    Static covers should not be used in favour of injection or lookup via the component manager. This cover will be removed in a later version of the Kernel

    public class SqlService
extends Object

    SqlService is a static Cover for the SqlService; see that interface for usage details.
